{
 "name": "RPlog_Johanna_Has_a_Ball_on_Bespin",
 "title": "Johanna's Ball on Bespin",
 "summary": "Johanna hosts a glittering ball in the Yarith Hotel ballroom on Cloud City, drawing together Jedi families, the Caspian contingent, and a crowd of teenagers -- among them Kiri Valios, Sabine, Sonja Damion, and the Imperium captain Kipran Jawatha, who sweeps Sonja onto the dance floor. The recovering newsman Loy Marin works the room with his protocol droid Bee, chasing a story among outlaws and Jedi alike, while the dark-skinned subplots simmer between Jessalyn, the apprehensive hosts, and the arriving Imperator Darth Malign with his unsettling Sith witch Quaye. Amid dancing, flirtation, propaganda sparring, and barely contained tension, Malign needles the Jedi and eventually sends his acolytes away, and the evening winds down with farewells. Far away, two salvagers recover a silent coffin-like pod from deep space, open it to find a goateed man with mismatched eyes -- and are never heard from again.",
